{"tid":2288161,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"建築工管打火機等工具被控 拘捕警員同意不覺被告曾作非法行為","createTime":"2020-11-16T09:51:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-16T10:41:30.000Z","uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"98ca2857fe201802b08fc8d6cd372c5387fdf462","tid":2288161,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-16T09:51:28.000Z","msg":"去年十一，反送中示威者在全港多處示威抗議「贈興」，全日警民衝突不斷。有年輕建築工人於屯門警方封鎖線附近被截查，搜出打火機氣油、打火機及士巴拿，被控管有物品意圖損壞財產罪。案件今於屯門裁判法院開審，辯方表明將爭議警方行動屬非法拘捕。負責拘捕警員於盤問時同意，拘捕前被告沒有作出任何非法行為。<br />\n<br />\n涉案警員張凱傑供稱，案發時被指派於屯門警署對開設立封鎖線，以支援其他於屯門市處理示威事件的同袍。行動期間，<span class=\"red\">他以私人電話觀看新聞直播</span>，得悉有警員被腐蝕液體灼傷，而他於封鎖線戒備時，發現被告及兩男兩女不時於封鎖線外數十米外一個轉角「偷望」警員。"},{"pid":"59d86db93b27a956b81aa0bdc0b0120baedee18f","tid":2288161,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-16T09:51:39.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201116/UF6OTWLQJZCETPADK5L57TAYLU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201116%2FUF6OTWLQJZCETPADK5L57TAYLU%2F&d=Mbax9TUBBsNKvtRo7%2B5fuwPtErjweJPees2C482IDEo%3D&h=c9aad5aa\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201116%2FUF6OTWLQJZCETPADK5L57TAYLU%2F&h=05f7d58a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201116/UF6OTWLQJZCETPADK5L57TAYLU/</a>"},{"pid":"1397b6032c5bc6a774fa8aae2ab73f931a902a1e","tid":2288161,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-16T09:59:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a82db78ba71db0fa85404466de68d602ce497112","tid":2288161,"uid":237425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-16T10:00:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"623a168bfdffe30aa6f2ebb8770759d54be3d73d","tid":2288161,"uid":38518,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-16T10:41:30.000Z","msg":"望下都拉屌那星"}]}